p-content/uploads/bizsem-logos1.jpg" width="700" height="108" /></p>\n<p>Hi and welcome to the 3 Door Digital website! We&#8217;re excited to be working with our good friends at <a href="http://goldfus-ins.co.il/" target="_blank">Goldfus Insurance &amp; Investments</a> and <a href="http://www.mercantile.co.il/wps/portal/mercantilehebrew" target="_blank">Mercantile Bank</a> to bring this event to fruition. We expect places to be taken quickly, so don&#8217;t miss out!</p>\n<p>The event will be in English and is suitable for the Legal and Real Estate sectors, but of course anyone is welcome to attend !</p>\n<p>Short presentations will be given on the following topics:</p>\n<p>3 Door Digital: <em>Want more clients? Maximise your Social Media presence</em></p>\n<p>Goldfus Insurance: <em>The implication of subrogation, inflation and how it all effects property ownership &#8211; How to protect property and liability </em></p>\n<p>Mercantile Bank: <em>From past to future, from west to east, global economic trends</em></p>\n<p>See you all on the 5th!</p>\n<p>Please complete the very short form below to confirm your attendance!</p>\n\n                <div class=''gf_browser_unknown gform_wrapper'' id=''gform_wrapper_9'' ><a id=''gf_9'' name=''gf_9'' class=''gform_anchor'' ></a><form method=''post'' enctype=''multipart/form-data'' target=''gform_ajax_frame_9'' id=''gform_9''  action=''/feed/#gf_9''>\n                        <div class=''gform_body''>\n                            <ul id=''gform_fields_9'' class=''gform_fields right_label description_below''><li id=''field_9_1'' class=''gfield               gfield_contains_required'' ><label class=''gfield_label'' for=''input_9_1''>Name<span class=''gfield_required''>*</span></label><div class=''ginput_container''><input name=''input_1'' id=''input_9_1'' type=''text'' value='''' class=''medium'' tabindex=''1'' /></div></li><li id=''field_9_2'' class=''gfield               gfield_contains_required'' ><label class=''gfield_label'