Door Digital works with both national and global brands, many of which have moved away from large marketing firms in order to benefit from our hands on and results driven approach.</p>\n<p>The available position is full time and office based. To find out more, simply click the job role below and more information will appear.</p>\n<div class="accordion" id="accordion2">\n<div class="accordion-group">\n<div class="accordion-heading" style="margin: 15px 0px 0px;">\n<a class="accordion-toggle" href="#collapseOne" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion2">Digital Outreach Consultant</a>\n</div>\n<div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-body collapse in">\n<div class="accordion-inner">\n<p>If you’re looking for a new, exciting position and your answer is ‘yes’ to the following questions, we want to hear from you:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Are you enthusiastic?</li>\n<li>Are you competitive?</li>\n<li>Are you creative?</li>\n<li>Do you want to succeed?</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong><strong><br />\nWhen joining us you commit to:<br />\n</strong></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Working hard</li>\n<li>Communicating effectively</li>\n<li>Contributing in a creative way</li>\n<li>Thinking outside the box</li>\n<li>Continuing to learn and develop &#8211; off your own back</li>\n<li>Joining us at the pub and on company night outs</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong><strong><br />\nIn return we will commit to:<br />\n</strong></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>An on-going training program and the backing of all our consultants.</li>\n<li>The potential to work with big brands</li>\n<li>A relaxed and fun working environment</li>\n<li>2 computer screens</li>\n<li>A company lunch once every 2 weeks</li>\n<li>Your birthday off</li>\n<li>+ many other office treats!</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong id="internal-source-marker_0.48900013556703925"><br />\nJob Description:</strong></p>\n<p>We are currently hiring a Digital Outreach Coordinator to join our growing team. The job involves a high level of internet searching as well as building relationships with webmasters, news sites and other online organisations. The successful candidate will be trained in the various aspects of SEO and link building and will become part of a small online marketing team. For those interested in working in SEO, 3 Door Digital  offers a great opportunity.<strong id="internal-source-marker_0.48900013556703925"></strong></p>\n<p>Skills / Experience:</p>\n<p><strong id="internal-source-marker_0.48900013556703925"></strong>A high level of English, both written and spoken<br />\nA good sales/marketing personality + Experience<br />\nInternet Proficiency in Email, Web-Browsing, Spreadsheets<br />\nThe ability to learn quickly and pick up new Internet skills, software, and web-tools.<br />\n<strong id="internal-source-marker_0.48900013556703925"><br />\nSalary</strong></p>\n<p>Dependent on Experience</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>To apply, simply fill out the form below. Good luck!</p>\n\n                <div class=''gf_browser_unknown gform_wrapper'' id=''gform_wrapper_4'' ><a id=''gf_4'' name=''gf_4'' class=''gform_anchor'' ></a><form method=''post'' enctype=''multipart/form-data'' target=''gform_ajax_frame_4'' id=''gform_4''  action=''/feed/#gf_4''>\n                        <div class=''gform_body''>\n                            <ul id=''gform_fields_4'' class=''gform_fields left_label description_below''><li id=''field_4_1'' class=''gfield               gfield_contains_required'' ><label class=''gfield_label'' for=''input_4_1_3''>Name<span class=''gfield_required''>*</span></label><div class=''ginput_complex ginput_container'' id=''input_4_1''><span id=''input_4_1_3_container'' class=''ginput_left''><input type=''text'' name=''input_1.3'' id=''input_4_1_3'' value='''' tabindex=''1'' /><label for=''input_4_1_3''>First</label></span><span id=''input_4_1_6_container'' class=''ginput_right''><input type=''text'' name=''input_1.6'' id=''input_4_1_6'' value='''' tabindex=''2'' /><label for=''input_4_1_6''>Last</label></s