cored 43 points in a pro-am game in Los Angeles, played in a celebrity soccer game in Washington, talked briefly with teams in Turkey and China about playing pro basketball there, and was headed to Europe for more paid appearances next week.</p>\n', 'Cavalier Clothing', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '374-revision', '', '', '2010-11-17 17:22:21', '2010-11-17 17:22:21', '', 374, 'http://gamers-live.net/blog/?p=961', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
